- Resolution: Default vault path set to ~/Documents/ObsidianVault; configurable in caaa.toml but requires restart to change.
6\. Defect: Embedded engine decision pending.
- Resolution: Selected SWI-Prolog (via C bindings) and Tiny Lisp (native Rust port) for deterministic rule checking.
